{{Italic title}} The '''''Journal of Zhejiang University''''' ([[Traditional Chinese]]: 浙江大學學報, [[Simplified Chinese]]: 浙江大学学报) is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] series published by the [[Zhejiang University Press]]. There are eight sub-journals, covering the fields of [[science]], [[engineering]], [[medicine]], [[humanities]], and [[social sciences]].
